	* nucleo/network/dnssd/DNSService.H: 
	* nucleo/network/dnssd/DNSServiceAnnouncer.*: 
	* nucleo/network/dnssd/DNSServiceBrowser.*: 
	New, DNS-SD-based, service discovery support

	* nucleo/network/rdv/*: 	
	* nucleo/plugins/howl/*: 
	These files are now obsolete and will be removed soon...
	
	* nucleo/nucleo.H.in: 
	* nucleo/nucleo.H: 
	Replaced the .H with a .H.in file that contains
	NUCLEO_SUPPORTS_XXX defines

