2005-11-30  Nicolas Roussel  <roussel@lri.fr>

	* nucleo/utils/AppUtils.cxx: 
	Added some black magic tricks that make the OS X nTest script
	obsolete (i.e. connects the nucleo process to the window server if
	it's not part of a bundle). Applications MUST call parseCommandLine
	for this magic to work...

	* nucleo/core/URI.H:
	Added a getQueryArg method for booleans.

